answerText: Assassin's Creed[10] North is Captain Martin Walker, who leads a Delta Force team into a ruined Dubai in search of Colonel Konrad, in this 2012 third-person shooter, which is based largely on Heart of Darkness.

question: Question: Answer the following about Nolan North's thousands of non-Uncharted voice-acting roles [10]  He voices Desmond Miles, whose murderous ancestors Altaïr Ibn-La'Ahad, Ezio Auditore, Ratonhnhaké:ton ("rah-doon-ha-gay-doon"), and Edward Kenway are the stars of this series of Ubisoft games.
